@startuml 05c_StateDiagram_Sample

skinparam backgroundColor #ffffff
skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor     #ffffff
    BorderColor         #000000
    BorderThickness     1.5
    FontName            Arial
    FontSize            11
    FontStyle           plain
    ArrowColor          #000000
    ArrowThickness      1.2
}
skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor     #ffffff
    BorderColor         #000000
    FontName            Arial
    FontSize            9
}
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial

' ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
title State 5.3 — SampleDTO  [SampleStatus]
' Source  : Samples.Status INT  CHECK (0,1,2,3)
' Enum    : SampleStatus  {New=0, Analyzing=1,
'                          Cancelled=2, Completed=3}
' DB Triggers on TestResults:
'   trg_TestResults_AutoWarning   → sets IsWarning = 1/0
'   trg_TestResults_AuditHistory  → inserts ResultHistory row
' ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

' ── States ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
state "New (0)" as New
state "Analyzing (1)" as Analyzing
state "Cancelled (2)" as Cancelled
state "Completed (3)" as Completed

' ── Initial → New ─────────────────────────────────────────────
[*] --> New : PlanningService.ConfigureSampleLocationsAsync()\n/ SampleRepository.AddSampleAsync()\n  EXEC sp_AddSample\n  [Status = 0, IsWarning = false]

' ── New → Analyzing (first test result entered) ───────────────
New --> Analyzing : TestingService.EnterTestResultAsync()\n/ TestResultRepository.SaveTestResultAsync()\n  EXEC sp_SaveTestResult\n  [Status = 1]

note on link
  DB TRIGGER trg_TestResults_AutoWarning fires:
  fn_IsResultExceedingLimit(paramId, value)
  → UPDATE Samples.IsWarning = 1 (if exceeds QCVN limit)

  DB TRIGGER trg_TestResults_AuditHistory fires:
  INSERT INTO ResultHistory (ResultID, OldValue, NewValue,
                             ChangedBy, ChangedAt)
end note

Analyzing --> Completed : All TestResults entered for this Sample\n[all required ParamIDs have ResultValue recorded]\n/ SampleRepository.UpdateSampleAsync(SampleDTO)\n  EXEC sp_UpdateSample  [Status = 3]

' ── New → Cancelled (planning cancels sample) ─────────────────
New --> Cancelled : PlanningService.CancelSampleAsync(sampleId)\n/ SampleRepository.UpdateSampleAsync(SampleDTO)\n  EXEC sp_UpdateSample  [Status = 2]

' ── Terminal states ────────────────────────────────────────────
Cancelled --> [*] : Sample discarded\n(read-only, excluded from PDF)
Completed --> [*] : Sample included in\nExportService.ExportStructuredPdfAsync()

' ── Notes ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
note right of Analyzing
  While Status = Analyzing (1):
  - Multiple TestResult entries
    may exist for this Sample
  - Each entry fires both triggers
  - IsWarning = true → row
    highlighted red in UI
    (EnterResultUC / LabResultUC)
end note

note right of Completed
  DB CHECK: Status IN (0,1,2,3)
  SampleStatus.Completed (3) means
  all parameters have results.
  Order.Status → Completed (2)
  when ALL its Samples reach
  SampleStatus.Completed (3).
end note

@enduml
